// 4.275 — `<img>` → `<Image>` migration on `/brands/[slug]` + `/` (homepage). Closes the 4 deferred `@next/next/no-img-element` warnings from v4.260. **What landed**: `app/brands/[slug]/page.tsx` brand-hero logo (line 255) + product-card image (line 399); `app/page.tsx` homepage product card (line 1025) + featured-brand logo tile (line 1271). Mirrors the greenlife-web pattern (already on `<Image>` for the same surfaces). External vendor logo/product URLs work because `next.config.ts` sets `images.remotePatterns: [{ protocol: "https", hostname: "**" }]` — no domain allowlist needed. Brand-logo Image uses `fill` + `unoptimized` (already-CDN-hosted, often SVG, no need for Next's resize pipeline); product Images use `fill` + `sizes` + `loading=\"lazy\"` for above-fold-aware responsive sizing. Customer-visible behavior identical pre/post — the `<img>` and `<Image fill>` both stretch into the wrapper's `relative overflow-hidden` parent. Lint at 0 errors + 0 warnings. tsc clean.
// 4.260 — Lint-hygiene mirror sweep from greenlife-web v3.345/v3.355/v3.360/v3.365/v3.385/v3.395. 17 files; lint dropped to 0 errors + 4 deferred `<img>` warnings (Image migration is a bigger refactor). Substantive changes: `components/AnnouncementBar.tsx` purity disable on Server-Component `Date.now()`; `app/menu/MenuFallback.tsx` purity disable on post-watchdog deal-end calc; `app/order/OrderMenu.tsx` stale-cart banner refactored to IIFE with single hoisted `nowMs`/`ageMs`/`days` (preserves outer-expression short-circuit + customer-visible copy); `app/account/orders/page.tsx` Seattle-only `hasJustReady` purity disable. Set-state-in-effect disables added on `DealCountdown`/`PaginatedProductsGrid`/`CartResumeBanner`/`MobileStickyCta`/`NeighborhoodMap`/`RecentlyViewedAutoStrip`. Unused-import drops on `account/profile/page.tsx` (`STORE`), `brands/[slug]/page.tsx` (`Link`), `2k-gardens.tsx` (`Link`), `avitas.tsx` (`BRAND_AMBER_LIGHT`), `bondi-farms.tsx` (`Image`). 17-line dead `buckets` useMemo dropped from `PaginatedProductsGrid.tsx`. Dead `eslint-disable` directives dropped on `find-your-strain/page.tsx` (2× `react/no-danger`) + `app/page.tsx` (`react-hooks/purity`). tsc clean.
